{"tid":270891,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟LOL比起DOTA既優勝之處係邊?","createTime":"2017-06-04T15:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T06:38:57.000Z","uid":49157,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ea174044af9ef63c7db73e560d03f35c18e789","tid":270891,"uid":49157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:35:10.000Z","msg":"明明係DOTA先起步 玩法唔敢講話一樣 但係都大同小異<br />\n但係出到o黎無論係利潤定人氣都贏dota成條街<br />\n所以究竟係因為LOL真係好玩過DOTA 定係RIOT用左o的咩營運手段贏DOTA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6277beea0d46fc7677c695c74110c3d7a5cdfaed","tid":270891,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"易玩 宣傳"},{"pid":"507f3bccf3ebafb202c40e3c0a9791ec0131e658","tid":270891,"uid":49157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>易玩 宣傳</blockquote><br />\n易玩唔敢講<br />\n但係dota宣傳差好多咩 點解又會咁差?<br />\n宜家主要宣傳/保住老玩家既都係twitch實況主/youtuber(e.g.nb3/sivhd)之類果o的<br />\ndota都有不過小好多 係純粹因為個game唔好玩定係佢地收左riot錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8ba99bc990f286aaa6fcb7f0ccfaa29c6308ce","tid":270891,"uid":49157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"587c71319287c26fc01e5992008a5b95d29ddb60","tid":270891,"uid":11862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"畫面啱小朋友/女仔多啲"},{"pid":"4c67f4fdc3d7562d0b014dc29165aff649300189","tid":270891,"uid":13843,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"Dota 2 啲畫風仲係好有 Warcraft 3 味"},{"pid":"a41a7f964b2ab4bb02a346146413e8ecd93e24f5","tid":270891,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dota 2 啲畫風仲係好有 Warcraft 3 味</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" 