d":16654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"頭啖湯"},{"pid":"debe57e0dfb8800525b68b0b9e8f3fd4bf406804","tid":270891,"uid":47945,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"其實係亞洲唔hit姐...<br />\n外國知名度一定係dota&gt;lol"},{"pid":"7dc259f4c37104fcd0f8c7a1b8522304dce96def","tid":270891,"uid":70272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得dota比lol難上手好多<br />\ndota要control既野比lol 多同複雜<br />\n玩過1xx 個鐘dota 都係好屎<br />\n跟住放棄玩番lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8393111d244126fde7bd663184d0873bd761b230","tid":270891,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dota 2 啲畫風仲係好有 Warcraft 3 味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都識/有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e96aaa7274a5caa7ee1173dbedddda3cc53fc4e","tid":270891,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"其實真係得香港少人玩Dota2<br />\n大陸都大把人玩dota2啦<br />\n海選果陣d大陸隊多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其中一個原因係頭啖湯<br />\n<br />\n第二係因為dota2係香港完全無宣傳<br />\n<br />\n其實難玩就真係唔難<br />\n只係太多變化<br />\n玩開lol就習慣左條路係直草叢就一汁同咁同對面互片<br />\nDota2 又要計樹林視野，又要計高低位，又要計時間搵野怪，有夜魔既話又要睇朝早定夜晚，又要防對家開霧，又要放眼放得好，又要防對家偷偷地食roshan，又要防人地o係你運緊野果陣殺信使....<br />\n<br />\n小朋友心智同手部未發育好<br />\n應負唔到，覺得難玩我都明既<br />\n<br />\n算啦"},{"pid":"40fd05efbef6b2914202e63b263bccaf3cc26f5a","tid":270891,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多野冇得解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正如大把歌手唱歌唔差外表唔差，但就係紅唔起</blockquote><br />\n係香港紅唔起姐 井底蛙"},{"pid":"f0ee7d79a9d80b701c8a2ebee80ae0a4244d2945","tid":270891,"uid":60622,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:29:45.000Z","msg":"lol中文化好似做得好過d2<br />\n<br />\nanyway香港人都唔撚會玩英文game嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7622a397ebd054f0fc60acaad7ffb5da0db4c7","tid":270891,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lol中文化好似做得好過d2<br />\n<br />\nanyway香港人都唔撚會玩英文game嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用開英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e68b3f8294d8cfccd396e0564307525472f6bca","tid":270891,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"香港人打機心態問題<br />\nDota＝少香港人玩＝少人玩＝無人陪玩＝唔好玩<br />\nlol＝多香港人玩＝多人玩＝有friend陪＝好好玩<br />\n<br />\n正如點解香港人淨係識3A大作一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568107806179fa03981cdec9f8379fb3416862a7","tid":270891,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"難上手，除左學生之外邊有人仲會投資成百粒鐘以上黎「學」玩隻game。<br />\n<br />\n起手5粒鐘玩唔出成就感已經GG。"},{"pid":"7c15420f54499cdc80c8ce10c291dcf0dcb07bf5","tid":270891,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難上手，除左學生之外邊有人仲會投資成百粒鐘以上黎「學」玩隻game。<br />\n<br />\n起手5粒鐘玩唔出成就感已經GG。</blockquote><br />\n心態唔同，鍾意打機覺得隻野值就會<br />\n以你心態黎講戰略game好多都唔會有生意"},{"pid":"db55d7dd988939b6695a02380796fca7523915e6","tid":270891,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>難上手，除左學生之外邊有人仲會投資成百粒鐘以上黎「學」玩隻game。<br />\n<br />\n起手5粒鐘玩唔出成就感已經GG。</blockquote><br />\n心態唔同，鍾意打機覺得隻野值就會<br />\n以你心態黎講戰略game好多都唔會有生意</blockquote><br />\n所以格鬥戰略game係小眾 越黎越縮"},{"pid":"0aebd1880303e926b020cd1a71a9fd3418197201","tid":270891,"uid":54368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>難上手，除左學生之外邊有人仲會投資成百粒鐘以上黎「學」玩隻game。<br />\n<br />\n起手5粒鐘玩唔出成