左去玩dota2.<br />\n感覺佢太有war3影子<br />\n我war3未出exp已經有玩<br />\n佢個英雄系統玩左太多年<br />\n太熟力敏智呢三個點數既影響<br />\n力敏智亦玩到好悶<br />\n玩左一陣就知影刺客同虛魔一定係後期一打五<br />\nT兵無論敵我都做足十隻<br />\n因為lv系統排埋d新手敵人俾我<br />\ntotal打左14x小時  勝率近7成<br />\n放棄了<br />\n<br />\nLoL有玩返  佢比較垃圾<br />\n但因為多fd玩 逼住一齊玩下<br />\n每次玩都好想做到一打五拎pentakill<br />\n每次都唔甘心一打三一打四但d隊友送肥敵人<br />\n一鋪又一鋪咁玩多左三年<br />\n最後都放棄左<br />\n<br />\ntotal黎講 lol個畫風 skin 都係娛樂性高d<br />\n<br />\n但要求打機質素  lol垃圾不如<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申  唔係我勁  係玩得太多年dota類型既game"},{"pid":"80d212db615e933c13aabf94db9d264966aee840","tid":270891,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"肥西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f0393dfca9c1f6a6b365e227d00e24f634fae6","tid":270891,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:50:46.000Z","msg":"我永遠都係果個問題 LOL入面攻擊自己隻卒會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce088f78ff552df4063de5b0efe3ed7be11e1057","tid":270891,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我永遠都係果個問題 LOL入面攻擊自己隻卒會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n攻擊到咩？<br />\nD垃圾驚連反補都冇"},{"pid":"6b872052f53df650426d8068b8159f30e1fdac9a","tid":270891,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc9eb4ee20e33d928724ff57efdaed489d1905b","tid":270891,"uid":47544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人打機心態問題<br />\nDota＝少香港人玩＝少人玩＝無人陪玩＝唔好玩<br />\nlol＝多香港人玩＝多人玩＝有friend陪＝好好玩<br />\n<br />\n正如點解香港人淨係識3A大作一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但lol係全球玩家人數都多過