/>\n令到lol成功係中國發展，集game 又易玩<br />\n畫風又比較貼近東方人，moba又易上癮<br />\n成個中國所有小朋友都玩lol<br />\nmarket share 一下子去到極大<br />\n所以數據上lol係高出dota好多<br />\n<br />\n始終dota係比較hardcore<br />\n難吸引新手"},{"pid":"5ff31a36531a7245ed99a37988a80e68c03ab11e","tid":270891,"uid":64146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係亞洲唔hit姐...<br />\n外國知名度一定係dota&gt;lol</blockquote><br />\n你嘅外國指邊度？ 我係美國住都唔覺有人提起dota</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無成日提起lol"},{"pid":"b9c6f95bc15f2cb9a2cdeff2f27dd6c5f1decef0","tid":270891,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"你要我玩成粒鐘然後輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242cc99688e7e27c7e2de5dfba8d0938ccc3787a","tid":270891,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lol中文化好似做得好過d2<br />\n<br />\nanyway香港人都唔撚會玩英文game嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人屌新細明體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c36c72d3ea3116b6b93e3fde9dc7288dd046fd","tid":270891,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"lol d女好j d"},{"pid":"fdde8a430bb338ffe0a8089c5f393a20c14ff343","tid":270891,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:27:29.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n個介面好唔user friendly<br />\nd野整到好亂"},{"pid":"323923a75fd26971453eca63f0ee12672cb7b692","tid":270891,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明係DOTA先起步 玩法唔敢講話一樣 但係都大同小異<br />\n但係出到o黎無論係利潤定人氣都贏dota成條街<br />\n所以究竟係因為LOL真係好玩過DOTA 定係RIOT用左o的咩營運手段贏DOTA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMarketing勁"},{"pid":"90b30c352cf2303f20a7711d6c908d90a20953ec","tid":270891,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"另外最近玩暴雪英霸<br />\n好玩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c3738d06c2da3e8d1301fd5c8accbb5dd7e84d","tid":270891,"uid":9217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"淨係講比賽<br />\nLOL係你唔識玩都睇得明佢地做緊咩<br />\nDOTA係你唔識玩就睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢到其實好吸引到新人加入"},{"pid":"1f15167a5d5e6aa9000d5e3e50386daa2808c321","tid":270891,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"Release Date都差左4年啦<br />\n未出LOL之前港台最紅既得信長同三國<br />\n本地war3 Dota玩家非常少<br />\n當然Dota應該係元祖級而且全世界最多人玩（？）<br />\n<br />\nLOL一出就食左呢批舊玩家先<br />\n再慢慢吸納新玩家先發到咁大<br />\n當年Garena(GGC)只係個war3老翻對戰平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中代理下一兩隻online game<br />\n<br />\n然後LOL係全世界大熱<br />\n其他人先如夢初醒發現PC競技遊戲呢條水"},{"pid":"73d3843a7bd979a65b28633bc2d09474faf3ea8b","tid":270891,"uid":8794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真<br />\n個介面好唔user friendly<br />\nd野整到好亂</blockquote><br />\n佢都唔係預你新人黎玩 好多野都係整比現有玩家玩<br />\n<br />\n所以一直keep到個市場"},{"pid":"61e5ec7dbf829242b15b67e636a9bd5b7b893487","tid":270891,"uid":8794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"其實dota既玩家人數好似係steam入面第一定第二位"},{"pid":"15c62313e592b68aed7c33a859abae8a12a6b2c3","tid":270891,"uid":95413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"dota2宣傳唔夠  當初本身大把人期待緊dota2出<br />\n但dota2就拖beta拖到仆街  <br />\nlol就食住個勢開s2世界賽宣傳  呢下已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\ndota難上手 正補反補高低位暗位<br />\n 呢樣大家公認   無咩好講<br />\n<br />\n重有就係dota老屎忽心態<br />\n人地宣傳一隻game係同人講隻game有咩優點  好玩在邊度  再去帶d新手一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ndota老屎忽唔同  佢地要同人講dota係最難玩既game<br />\n玩開lol既玩家都係低能仔  永遠唔會識玩dota之類<br />\n所以叫玩開lol既人唔好玩dota<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都唔明點解有部份dota撚會以踩其他game黎拎優越感咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661aaad53e75bfdf13bfc4125437bf58021e4c6a","tid":270891,"uid":1997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我永遠都係果個問題 LOL入面攻擊自己隻卒會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n攻擊到咩？<br />\nD垃圾驚連反補都冇</blockquote><br />\n咁威呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca268c0aedc0fe100e2af5799de6f80ead57864","tid":270891,"uid":64146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dota2宣傳唔夠  當初本身大把人期待緊dota2出<br />\n但dota2就拖beta拖到仆街  <br />\nlol就食住個勢開s2世界賽宣傳  呢下已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\ndota難上手 正補反補高低位暗位<br />\n 呢樣大家公認   無咩好講<br />\n<br />\n重有就係dota老屎忽心態<br />\n人地宣傳一隻game係同人講隻game有咩優點  好玩在邊度  再去帶d新手一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ndota老屎忽唔同  佢地要同人講dota係最難玩既game<br />\n玩開lol既玩家都係低能仔  永遠唔會識玩dota之類<br />\n所以叫玩開lol既人唔好玩dota<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都唔明點解有部份dota撚會以踩其他game黎拎優越感咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無辦法，數據上唔夠人講，唯有用其它野補救<br />\n而且dota無論如何都係玄門正宗，係會有d優越感"}]}